      "date": "2020-11-26 17:55:44.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThe loop was removed because at the time we thought that we could read the maximum allowed value and use that instead of a trial and error procedure. This was done as we were looking at some issues with OPA. In OPA the value read is a true maximum, which should always be honoured. However, on MLX that's not the case.",
